author: MATTHEW WEAVER Capital Press
title: Fertilizer plant reopens after 2022 fire | Washington | capitalpress.com
text: MOSES LAKE, Wash. — Teamwork kept workers at a Wilbur-Ellis fertilizer plant in Moses Lake, Wash., delivering to farmers after a devastating October 2022 fire, company leaders say. The facility was a complete loss, spokesman Aaron Dunajeski said.
